title: Transformation At Another World During Rebirth - Novel Updates
author: 鬼君
description: The leader (Squid) did not think that when he was bragging about his achievements, Yue Yue would actually come and attack his fortress! The fortress wall tremble from the heavy blow. Peng–! The loud sound startled the citizens. “En? What is happening?! What happened?! The happy leader (Squid) places down his bowl of wine, rushing out to only hear shouting-“Sir Squid, we’re under attack! We do not know who are the attackers…”>
